{"tid":506814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]去女朋友屋企食冬至飯 好似得罪伯母","createTime":"2017-12-22T14:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T11:49:49.000Z","uid":137291,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5427d2d75f8c9ac953c364c2c3deae0826ee3a4d","tid":506814,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今晚去咗伯母屋企食飯<br />\n咁好正常就邊食飯邊傾計啦<br />\n傾傾吓傾到香港多人自殺之類<br />\n跟住條女又拉埋隻韓狗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我忍唔住講咗句<br />\n&quot;死咗隻韓狗姐, 有咩大不了&quot;<br />\n<br />\n跟住我地全場dead air曬<br />\n我女朋友呆咗望住我<br />\n我問佢咩事<br />\n跟住佢望向伯母<br />\n我發現伯母啤住我<br />\n係怒視嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後成餐飯伯母都冇再講過嘢<br />\n係得我女朋友周不時講吓一兩句嘢<br />\n但係我都唔夠膽講多<br />\n淨係夠膽講覆一兩隻字例如唔該 好呀之類<br />\n但氣氛好可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n伯母自己食完粒聲唔出自己入返房<br />\n淨返我 我女朋友 世伯三個喺出面繼續食<br />\n<br />\n食完餐飯我就直接走咗<br />\n唔夠膽再做留低或者見到伯母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打請問我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪得罪咗伯母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3129d7aea4f283cf1c0ac75312a55395ffd219ba","tid":506814,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"55b3eba06e045fa6f9e6a975bba3fdf0707517aa","tid":506814,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1/10</blockquote><br />\n認真架屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ca8f1d9d93975443ef6a2884375c7b2a7b2eda","tid":506814,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"宜家好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知以後點面對佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" clas